Text:
If you like NFSU, you will like this.
I prefer FlatOut...

But thx anyway
when installing the game it crashes at 'instantiating texture dictionary' ?!?!?!?!

can anyone seed??  please 
it stopped at 99%
every time i download this game it stops at 99%,why?

It stops at 99% because no one is seeding. What happens is that when people finish the download, they don't seed. With no seeders, the leechers share between themselves and total up to a certain percent. Since everyone is stuck, they go to the comments and spam "SEED PLZ".

I'm stuck at 98.7%. I'd be at 99% if *you* were sharing.
..and then when someone *does* seed and that user finishes the download, *they* don't seed and everyone gets stuck again.
